Class 1 - Cucumber

Cucumber - it is a tool that supports BDD

Given- Pre condition.
When- To perform actions.
And- Supporting tag.
Then- Expected result/outcome

US- 12345

Given user able to open chrome browser
When user enters username and password
And user clicks on login button
Then user is navigated to dashboard page
When user clicks on PIM option
And user clicks on employee list option
When user enter name in the employee name field
And user clocks on search button
Then user is able to see the employee

2345- Search employee by id

Given user able to open chrome browser
When user enters username and password
And user clicks on login button
Then user is navigated to dashboard page
When user clicks on PIM option
And user clicks on employee list option
When user enter name in the employee id field
And user clocks on search button
Then user is able to see the employee

-- Cucumber encourages code reusability concept __

Main Folder - the code we write to develop the application, we write under main
Develop the application
To test the application

Test Folder - the code we write to test the aplication, we write under test

Two things we have in every project

- Code - Java
- None Code - Java

Coding will be at one place
Non java will be at another place

Valid admin login
Given user is navigated to HRMS application
When user enters admin username and password
Then admin user is successfully logged in





